{"tid":248333,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大鄉里出城 去意大利有少少問題想請教","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T03:09:28.000Z","uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"288b074f2f42060af5b27c02f2ffd3aefb83ccc9","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"就咁既<br />\n我同個同事打算9月尾去意大利玩9日8夜<br />\n有一個問題出現左<br />\n就係火車票問題<br />\n想問一問訂同即場買火車飛 個價錢爭幾遠？<br />\n如果即場買飛 會唔會因為架火車full左而買唔到？<br />\n我同事怕訂左會限死哂d時間<br />\n我就怕唔訂會貴左好多同怕會買唔到飛<br />\n除左呢樣仲有咩要注意？<br />\n有冇人又係9月尾去意大利玩呢？"},{"pid":"8dc931646c39bb69b26060011a0e63203f351c70","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0231b83b3317708ebd1cc1a28165c70c6dfbfe40","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"之前去過<br />\n訂同即買分別係你有無discount code<br />\n無discount無分別<br />\n你去前google下<br />\n訂過飛嘅會定期收到discount code"},{"pid":"b00dfe7bd578a042be9755dd80a75543f2fd8d57","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去過<br />\n訂同即買分別係你有無discount code<br />\n無discount無分別<br />\n你去前google下<br />\n訂過飛嘅會定期收到discount code</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網上搵到嘅教學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sharpelawtravel.com/?p=824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sharpelawtravel.com%2F%3Fp%3D824&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6c401680\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sharpelawtravel.com/?p=824</a>"},{"pid":"aca28e5f3cd149de6fd9a108e988793a8a45e83c","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去過<br />\n訂同即買分別係你有無discount code<br />\n無discount無分別<br />\n你去前google下<br />\n訂過