full到買唔到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你去邊<br />\n佢部分火車有分唔同class<br />\n價錢可以差幾倍<br />\n訂定可以揀火車型號同sure有平class票買<br />\n講discount code<br />\n你可以定期google trenitalia discount code<br />\n有時有d人會放上網畀人<br />\n我果次因為買平機票<br />\n得2個星期準備所以等唔切discount code<br />\n<br />\n無記錯你就咁登記都做到會員</blockquote><br />\n其實我都係大路羅馬去佛羅倫斯 再去威尼斯 最後去米蘭<br />\n然後番香港<br />\n同埋而家訂飛我見佢唔做會員都訂得 好似都幾方便<br />\n咁係咪訂左先好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係羅馬去佛羅倫斯<br />\n再喺佛羅倫斯來回比薩<br />\n最後返羅馬回香港<br />\n<br />\n訂咗會收到email<br />\n去前印出嚟同埋轉做pdf<br />\n去到show印出嚟or手機開pdf都okay<br />\n做埋會員會check到班火車有無遲<br />\n(不過果陣要睇意大利文，家陣唔知)"},{"pid":"ee89c84295aeeda58a60b5d3268be7ae2d23278f","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/231412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F231412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ce579ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n望返<br />\n好似discount code跟人<br />\n你一係先訂一程<br />\n做咗會員<br />\n<br />\n再慢慢等佢send宣傳畀你<br />\n話唔定喺你出發前會收到你嘅discount code"},{"pid":"faf683cfb6ae70e8561080f224421d782bb03581","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/231412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F231412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ce579ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n望返<br />\n好似discount code跟人<br />\n你一係先訂一程<br />\n做咗會員<br />\n<br />\n再慢慢等佢send宣傳畀你<br />\n話唔定喺你出發前會收到你嘅discount code</blockquote><br />\n唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26e458e18954cfffc331f0ea2b814e45ef62405","tid":248333,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"但好似係網站訂飛, 結果你遲到既話係無得改班次"},{"pid":"ef93cdbbc500e3d212698848ab8f6e35451fa0bd","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但好似係網站訂飛, 結果你遲到既話係無得改班次</blockquote><br />\n我都有上網睇過 好難改好麻煩<br />\n我同事就係怕俾呢樣局限左"},{"pid":"7265588b7824ccc05f36403944deb87b89e9b728","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但好似係網站訂飛, 結果你遲到既話係無得改班次</blockquote><br />\n我都有上網睇過 好難改好麻煩<br />\n我同事就係怕俾呢樣局限左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你諗你<br />\n外國好少delay<br />\nd車會一準備好夠鐘出發<br />\n你話你同事怕局限<br />\n<br />\n但知唔知人地有d火車一日成朝得一班，再等就要下午先有車<br />\n你執完行李慢慢去到先買飛<br />\n一來唔知有無平飛<br />\n二來買唔切等成個上午到下午先有一班<br />\n<br />\n學習下分事情先後次序重要性好過啦"},{"pid":"e3d3aaee3569168c0907313405b82b2fd2457a5f","tid":248333,"uid":11124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:22:10.000Z","msg":"上次去預早網上訂 冇discount code 都平過即場買一截"},{"pid":"5185008d77be08b1618b1b5dd4dc0d2ac374275e","tid":248333,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"咁睇黎訂好d"},{"pid":"65a66663714138e8a2129a9f574f2a5233f55ba2","tid":248333,"uid":21122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"其實早鳥優惠係平好多<br />\n因為早鳥嘅traniltalty（好似係咁串）可以15歐買到頭等<br />\n<br />\n早1個月，econ class 一程大約30歐<br />\n<br />\n但即場都ok, 因為d火車去大城市都只係1個鐘一班，算好密<br />\n<br />\n最差情況係econ 賣晒，到時你要買biz class or first class, 價錢係60-120歐一程<br />\n<br />\n但如果你冇信心，咪plan好行程做多d功課<br />\n預好時間然後上網買，你仲可以有國際學生優惠（平5-10歐）"},{"pid":"bdafe60cc26706493e87157caab784826000ae7d","tid":248333,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"近既Regional既即場買就得<br />\n但兩個大城市中間d快車 就早買會平好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740e64783029f1c896d91002833823435ede747f","tid":248333,"uid":107417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"一定要預早訂<br />\ntrenitalia早訂平好多<br />\n即場買好很貴"},{"pid":"fc3aa38fba15730ad0b581b1c6cf36b583c5fa1a","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要預早訂<br />\ntrenitalia早訂平好多<br />\n即場買好很貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係咁<br />\n<br />\nsor9 樓主<br />\n我之前因為出發前兩星期先買到機票<br />\n所以唔知早幾個月買會平<br />\n啱啱google見人話預訂4個月內車票<br />\n越遲就越少優惠<br />\n越早就越平<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.qyer.com/bbs/thread-1092895-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.qyer.com%2Fbbs%2Fthread-1092895-1.html&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d3758ef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.qyer.com/bbs/thread-1092895-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"f196c9482125a2b1f5e48dda671b6a980e1d1918","tid":248333,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返<br />\n應該係15年3月先開始有呢個早鳥優惠<br />\n我去係13年1月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a152dcc18af0329c8630fa9b64f3a4e0636e06","tid":248333,"uid":65104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"果次係羅馬睇錯mon miss左原本訂好左去pisa既班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到要即場買下班車<br />\n係貴好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ce67e882c8498842cff63cdbedd201b1f4c364","tid":248333,"uid":59407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"預早book 平好多<br />\n我個時去大城市之間既火車一早book定<br />\n其實都會方便d<br />\n唔洗到時再睇班次同預價錢<br />\n特別旺季 平飛好快冇晒"},{"pid":"0392110d35533788c3fa45967c67980b28c1bb41","tid":248333,"uid":67635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"上個月先去完，我早幾個月前訂，我全部買早鳥優惠，計返差唔多慳一半"},{"pid":"b1b7fd50ceebe6